uima.cas.Sofa.sofaString: INDICATION: ___ year old woman with COPD, productive cough, rales left base, and bilat. Previously described right tracheal deviation is not seen on the current study. Unchanged bilateral apical bronchial thickening. The lungs are otherwise clear without focal consolidation, pneumothorax, or effusion. No acute cardiopulmonary process, without consolidation or evidence of CHF.
